<subSubSection pageId="9" pageNumber="37" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1437,152,1298]" pageId="9" pageNumber="37">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,343,1031,1057]" pageId="9" pageNumber="37">Etymology:</emphasis>
The specific epithet is a patronym honoring Marcelo T. Tavares, professor and researcher of 
<taxonomicName box="[151,291,1072,1098]" class="Insecta" family="Chalcididae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Chalcididae</taxonomicName>
at Universidade Federal do Espírito Santo, 
<collectingCountry box="[803,878,1072,1098]" name="Brazil" pageId="9" pageNumber="37">Brazil</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1437,152,1298]" pageId="9" pageNumber="37">
